"Test $Mesh function — Cantilever Wall Q4
'<hr/>
'<h4>Mesh generation</h4>
'Cantilever wall: 4m wide, 3m tall, 2x2 mesh
a = 4'm
b = 3'm
n_a = 2
n_b = 2
n_j = (n_a + 1)*(n_b + 1)
n_e = n_a*n_b

'Joint coordinates
x_j = [0; 0; 0; 2; 2; 2; 4; 4; 4]
y_j = [0; 1.5; 3; 0; 1.5; 3; 0; 1.5; 3]

'Element connectivity (4 elements, 4 nodes each)
e_j = [1; 4; 5; 2 | 2; 5; 6; 3 | 4; 7; 8; 5 | 5; 8; 9; 6]

'Supported joints (base: 1, 4, 7)
s_j = [1; 4; 7]

'Loaded joints (lateral at top: negative = lateral arrow)
f_j = [-3; -6; -9]

'<h4>Mesh visualization</h4>
$Mesh{x_j; y_j; e_j; s_j; f_j @ w = 300}
